mitives.\"}]}, {\"id\": \"devops\", \"d\": \"cs\", \"col\": 11, \"row\": 7, \"l\": \"DevOps & SRE\", \"books\": [{\"a\": \"Beyer et al.\", \"t\": \"Site Reliability Engineering (free online)\", \"n\": \"Google's SRE book. The standard.\"}, {\"a\": \"Humble & Farley\", \"t\": \"Continuous Delivery\", \"n\": \"CI/CD foundations. Rigorous.\"}, {\"a\": \"Kim et al.\", \"t\": \"The Phoenix Project\", \"n\": \"Conceptual narrative. Read first for motivation.\"}]}, {\"id\": \"compprog\", \"d\": \"cs\", \"col\": 9, \"row\": 5, \"l\": \"Competitive programming\", \"books\": [{\"a\": \"Halim\", \"t\": \"Competitive Programming 3\", \"n\": \"The standard contest preparation book.\"}, {\"a\": \"Laaksonen\", \"t\": \"Competitive Programmer's Handbook (free)\", \"n\": \"Excellent free alternative.\"}, {\"a\": \"Skiena & Revilla\", \"t\": \"Programming Challenges\", \"n\": \"Problem-focused. Good variety.\"}]}, {\"id\": \"elec_fund\", \"d\": \"hw\", \"col\": 11, \"row\": 1, \"l\": \"Electronics fundamentals\", \"books\": [{\"a\": \"Horowitz & Hill\", \"t\": \"The Art of Electronics\", \"n\": \"The bible of practical electronics. Mandatory.\"}, {\"a\": \"Hayt & Kemmerly\", \"t\": \"Engineering Circuit Analysis\", \"n\": \"Rigorous circuit theory foundation.\"}, {\"a\": \"Nilsson & Riedel\", \"t\": \"Electric Circuits\", \"n\": \"Standard circuit analysis text.\"}]}, {\"id\": \"analog\", \"d\": \"hw\", \"col\": 11, \"row\": 2, \"l\": \"Analog circuits\", \"books\": [{\"a\": \"Horowitz & Hill\", \"t\": \"The Art of Electronics (analog chapters)\", \"n\": \"Op-amps, BJTs, FETs \\u2014 practical and deep.\"}, {\"a\": \"Sedra & Smith\", \"t\": \"Microelectronic Circuits\", \"n\": \"Standard analog IC design text.\"}, {\"a\": \"Razavi\", \"t\": \"Design of Analog CMOS Integrated Circuits\", \"n\": \"Graduate-level analog IC. Very rigorous.\"}]}, {\"id\": \"digital\", \"d\": \"hw\", \"col\": 11, \"row\": 3, \"l\": \"Digital logic\", \"books\": [{\"a\": \"Wakerly\", \"t\": \"Digital Design