ocs for the best free PCB CAD tool.\"}]}, {\"id\": \"rf\", \"d\": \"hw\", \"col\": 12, \"row\": 6, \"l\": \"RF & SDR\", \"books\": [{\"a\": \"ARRL\", \"t\": \"The ARRL Handbook for Radio Communications\", \"n\": \"The comprehensive RF/antenna practical reference.\"}, {\"a\": \"Pozar\", \"t\": \"Microwave Engineering\", \"n\": \"Rigorous microwave theory.\"}, {\"a\": \"Balanis\", \"t\": \"Antenna Theory: Analysis and Design\", \"n\": \"The antenna theory standard.\"}]}, {\"id\": \"sysadmin\", \"d\": \"hw\", \"col\": 11, \"row\": 6, \"l\": \"Linux & homelab\", \"books\": [{\"a\": \"Ward\", \"t\": \"How Linux Works\", \"n\": \"Best internals-oriented Linux book.\"}, {\"a\": \"Shotts\", \"t\": \"The Linux Command Line (free)\", \"n\": \"Command line mastery. Free online.\"}, {\"a\": \"Limoncelli, Hogan & Chalup\", \"t\": \"The Practice of System and Network Administration\", \"n\": \"Comprehensive sysadmin reference.\"}]}, {\"id\": \"testmeas\", \"d\": \"hw\", \"col\": 12, \"row\": 3, \"l\": \"Test & measurement\", \"books\": [{\"a\": \"Tektronix\", \"t\": \"ABCs of Oscilloscopes (free PDF)\", \"n\": \"Instrument fundamentals. Start here.\"}, {\"a\": \"Horowitz & Hill\", \"t\": \"The Art of Electronics (measurement chapters)\", \"n\": \"Practical measurement craft.\"}, {\"a\": \"Williams\", \"t\": \"The Circuit Designer's Companion\", \"n\": \"Practical analog design and debugging.\"}]}, {\"id\": \"search\", \"d\": \"ai\", \"col\": 14, \"row\": 3, \"l\": \"Search & heuristics\", \"books\": [{\"a\": \"Russell & Norvig\", \"t\": \"Artificial Intelligence: A Modern Approach ch.3\\u20135\", \"n\": \"BFS, DFS, A*, IDA*, adversarial search.\"}, {\"a\": \"Nilsson\", \"t\": \"Principles of Artificial Intelligence\", \"n\": \"Older but more rigorous on search.\"}, {\"a\": \"Pearl\", \"t\": \"Heuristics\", \"n\": \"Deep theoretical treatment of A* and admissibility.\"}]}, {\"id\": \"csp\", \"d\": \"ai\", \"col\": 14, \"row\": 4, \"l\": \"Constraint satisfaction\", \"books\": [{\"